OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,FMore than 60 babies in the UK have
OL,7,Ffallen ill with symptoms consistent
OL,8,Fwith being fed toxic formula,
OL,9,Ffollowing the recall of multiple
OL,10,Fproducts earlier this year.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fis investigating the cases, which
OL,14,Finvolve 35 male babies and 26 female,
OL,15,Ffrom across the country. The majority
OL,16,Fof the cases were in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
