OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,FNestle recalled multiple batches of 12
OL,7,FSMA Infant Formula and Follow-On
OL,8,FFormula from UK shops at the start of
OL,9,FJanuary, due to the possible presence
OL,10,Fof cereulide toxin.
OL,12,FDanone, another widely distributed
OL,13,Finfant formula manufacturer, then
OL,14,Frecalled one batch of Aptamil First
OL,15,FInfant Formula over cereulide
OL,16,Fcontamination later the same month.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
