OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772752278
OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,FThis was then extended to include 15
OL,7,Fproducts of Cow & Gate First Infant
OL,8,FMilk and Follow on Milk formula, as
OL,9,Fwell as further Aptamil products.
OL,11,FThe UKHSA said it had been notified of
OL,12,F61 cases where children had eaten
OL,13,Fcontaminated batches and gone on to
OL,14,Fhave "symptoms consistent with
OL,15,Fcereulide toxin poisoning".
OL,17,FThe toxin can cause vomiting, stomach
OL,18,Fcramping and diarrhea, and is highly
OL,19,Fheat stable, meaning boiling or
OL,20,Fcooking a product won't destroy it,
OL,21,Fthe Food Standards Agency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
