FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772752278
OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,FMost cases resolve without treatment
OL,7,Fwithin 24 hours, providing there is no
OL,8,Fongoing exposure.
OL,10,F"Given the widespread availability of
OL,11,Fthese products prior to the recalls,
OL,12,Fthis is not unexpected," Gauri
OL,13,FGodbole, Deputy Director,
OL,14,FGastrointestinal Infections, Food
OL,15,FSafety and One Health at UKHSA, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
