PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772752278
OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,F"Testing of the recalled formula has
OL,7,Fconfirmed presence of the toxin in
OL,8,Fsome batches at levels that exceed
OL,9,Flimits set by the European Food Safety
OL,10,FAuthority and therefore pose a
OL,11,Fpotential health risk.
OL,13,F"Parents and caregivers are advised to
OL,14,Frecheck and remove all recalled
OL,15,Fformula from their homes to prevent
OL,16,Fillness in their children."
OL,18,FIn a statement shared with ITV News,
OL,19,FDanone reassured parents that all of
OL,20,Ftheir infant formula currently on sale
OL,21,Fis safe to consume.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
