CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772752278
OL,3,CMore than 60 babies fall ill after
OL,4,Cconsuming toxic formula, UKHSA says
OL,6,F"To date there are no confirmed cases
OL,7,Fof sickness or symptoms linked to our
OL,8,Fproducts," the statement said.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Nestle told ITV
OL,11,FNews: "We are very sorry to hear about
OL,12,Fthese cases and our teams will work
OL,13,Fclosely with any families who report
OL,14,Fthese types of concerns to us."
OL,16,FSee the full list of recalled batches
OL,17,Fto avoid:
